Subject: Yang-Mills Construction Relevance Gate

Description: Project-local math tool for separating construction-relevant Yang-Mills mechanisms from gap-stage intuition, physical analogy, and source-symbolic metaphor.

& [YangMillsConstructionRelevanceGate] is a math inquiry tool
  + [tool_uuid] is 637e6ec3-8a01-4320-9780-ab3060ee7c36
  + [problem] is Yang-Mills Existence and Mass Gap
  + [created_at] is 2026-06-26
  + [trigger_record] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\events\proof_inquiry\2026-06-26_yang_mills_construction_route_reopen_001.sop
  + [role] is classify whether a proposed idea advances stages 001-006 of construction, stages 007-008 of gap transfer, or only intuition
  + [not_role] is proving Yang-Mills, validating lattice-only evidence as continuum proof, or treating sealed-curvature metaphor as a regularized model

& [GateColumnSet] is the construction-relevance surface
  + [candidate] is the proposed mechanism or route
  + [defined_objects] is lattice action, continuum measure, Schwinger functions, observables, Hamiltonian, correlation estimate, or none
  + [construction_stage_contact] is regularization, uniform estimates, continuum limit, OS properties, reconstruction, nontriviality, gap mechanism, gap transfer, or none
  + [proof_artifact_needed] is the next theorem or construction required
  + [source_fit] is how sealed curvature or curvature packet language maps, if at all
  + [relevance_class] is construction_relevant, gap_relevant_after_construction, heuristic_relevant, or outside
  + [first_gap] is the first route-stage lock blocking proof-shaped promotion

& [UseProcedure] is the gate workflow
  + [step_001_name_candidate] is identify the proposed Yang-Mills mechanism
  + [step_002_check_defined_objects] is list actual mathematical objects defined
  + [step_003_score_stage_contact] is mark which construction or gap stage is touched
  + [step_004_identify_artifact] is name the theorem, estimate, measure, or reconstruction still needed
  + [step_005_classify_relevance] is classify relevance and first gap

  = must: classify construction stages before gap-stage language
  = must: require defined observables before correlation decay claims
  = must: require reconstruction before spectral gap transfer
  = should: preserve sealed-curvature intuition as a stage-007 target when construction exists
  - never: let gap intuition skip existence of the continuum quantum field theory

(yang_mills_construction_relevance_gate) :candidate: /objects, route stage, proof artifact/ |gap-intuition-overclaim|
  + [inside] is construction relevance classification
  + [boundary] is intuition can guide stage 007 without advancing stages 001-006
  |outside| metaphor as model, finite-lattice claim as continuum construction, and confinement language as mass-gap proof
